{"tid":1138402,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"只係分咗手一日  已經成日忍唔住想搵佢","createTime":"2019-05-04T13:24:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-04T16:11:40.000Z","uid":60293,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"67ea78c2613491328a4b27732d5dd9f140314240","tid":1138402,"uid":60293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T13:24:39.000Z","msg":"我地起碼有十年<br />\n本來都好地地 直到呢一年開始慢慢有啲野唔同咗<br />\n我都唔知點講 係對佢會有種好厭倦嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為我覺得佢變咗<br />\n以前好單純 同佢會互相分享大家日常生活開心唔開心既大小事 <br />\n但唔知幾時開始佢變到好勢利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下下都要計住計住  好似我做乜都係要為咗佢 仲對佢有利先得 我好似變咗佢個工具咁 <br />\n有冇人明我感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有幾次我想斬纜 但個人好似上咗癮咁離唔開佢 要每日長期有佢係身邊先安樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n直到琴日我先成功迫自己要離開佢<br />\n然後將所有野刪哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我以為只要夠決絕就可以 但原來唔係咁的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日我已經有十幾次想搵番佢既念頭...<br />\n點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我唔想再陷入呢個深淵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我真係唔想再上fb ig<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好無益<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=